How did you know that?          

02:35.755 --> 02:39.724
     I could tell               
     by the way he smiled at me.

02:39.726 --> 02:40.792
              Oh.               

02:40.794 --> 02:43.461
Why ain't supper                
on the table here, huh?         

02:43.463 --> 02:45.630
              Well, can you wait
