Edith, where's the aspirin?     
I have a head coming on.        

02:59.012 --> 03:00.311
                  It's upstairs.

03:00.313 --> 03:03.148
Why is it always upstairs       
when I'm downstairs             

03:03.150 --> 03:04.382
and downstairs                  
when I'm upstairs?              

03:04.384 --> 03:06.017
Can't you never organize        
nothing, Edith, huh?            

03:06.019 --> 03:07.318
                    Oh, well,   
                    I'll get it.

03:07.320 --> 03:09.453
No, no, no, don't bother.       
I'll get the aspirin.           

03:09.455 --> 03:11.422
Get supper                      
on the table, huh?              

03:11.424 --> 03:13.825
    Jeez, one of these days     
 I'm gonna come home from work  

03:13.827 --> 03:15.626
    and I'm gonna reach out     
          my two hands          

03:15.628 --> 03:17.628
    to get the things           
     that I need and I want     

03:17.630 --> 03:18.696
and I'm gonna find them...      

03:20.532 --> 03:22.767
Oh, hello,                      
Gloria.                         

03:22.769 --> 03:24.869
How was your day                
at work?                        

